Class MergeAdapter

    • org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor

  • public class MergeAdapter
extends org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
    This class is responsible for merging two class files based on the merging strategies in the JReFrameworker framework. References: http://www.jroller.com/eu/entry/merging_class_methods_with_asm
